 על הפולינום 
\begin_inset Formula $x^{2}+1$
\end_inset

:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x^{2}+1\to x^{3}+x^{2}+x\to x^{2}+x+1\to x^{3}\to x^{2}\to x\to1
\]

\end_inset

כלומר 
\begin_inset Formula $T^{6}\left(x^{2}+1\right)=1$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

